Figure 2. Tubulin purification from the Paramecium cell extract, illustrated by Coomassie blue staining (CB) and immunoreactivity with TAP 952 and AXO 49. Cytoplasmic extract before (lanes 1, 4, and 6) and after (lane 2) taxol treatment; purified tubulin (lanes 3, 5, and 7). Protein amounts: lanes 1 and 2, 25 m g; lanes 4 and 6, 20 m g; lane 3, 2 m g; lanes 5 and 7, 0.5 m g. 